actionAppleScript.inline:
tell application "Finder"
 shut down end tell

tell application "System Events"
key code 23 using {command down, shift down} end tell

longActionAppleScript.inline:
tell application "System Events"
key code 20 using {command down, shift down} end tell

source.inline: set cpu to do shell script "ps axo %cpu | awk '{s+=$1}END{print s}'"return cpu & "%"
